Package: institutions
Title: Global Research Identifier Database (GRID)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Markus",
           family = "Skyttner",
           role = c("cre", "aut"),
           email = "markussk@kth.se")
Description: The grid.ac website provides open data on
    institutions around the world under the CC0 license. This R package
    downloads the data and generates a SQLite3 db, making data available
    with full text search capabilities to use from R.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/KTH-Library/institutions
